//www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Alex-Wolff-and-Billie-Eilish-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Alex-Wolff-and-Billie-Eilish-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Alex-Wolff-and-Billie-Eilish-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>亚历克斯·沃尔夫 (Alex Wolff) 谈到与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish)</a>产生“音乐火花”，促成了他们目前的巡演。</p><p>这位<em>遗传</em>演员与他的兄弟 Nat 和 Alex Wolff 的音乐项目正在 Eilish 正在进行的“Hit Me Hard and Soft”巡演中拉开帷幕，而三人最近合作了单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-nat-alex-wolffs-new-single-soft-kissing-hour-with-vocals-from-billie-eilish-3802162">“Soft Kissing Hour”</a> 。</p><p>沃尔夫在接受<a href="https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-features/alex-wolff-fraternity-movie-the-line-oppenheimer-1236050683/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《好莱坞报道》</em></a>采访时详细介绍了他和艾利什在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/oscars">奥斯卡颁奖典礼</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/coachella">科切拉音乐节上</a>的交情，并承认他“不太确定”这位“羽毛之鸟”歌手之前是否是他们音乐的粉丝。</p><p> “我们刚刚在奥斯卡颁奖典礼上认识并一拍即合，然后在科切拉度过了一个周末，我们来回播放歌曲，”他回忆道。 “音乐火花迸发出来，这是一种直接的联系。 </p><p><iframe title="Nat 和 Alex Wolff - 轻柔接吻时间（官方展示台）" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Of_Y5SFJtk0?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “然后纳特（沃尔夫）给她播放了他的新歌《温柔的接吻时刻》，她只是说，‘哦，我想制作那首歌。’”所以我们真的很幸运，她制作了这首歌并演唱了它，这是我们制作的最喜欢的歌曲之一。”</p><p>沃尔夫称“能与她成为朋友并与她一起演奏音乐是我的荣幸”，并补充道：“这是一个千载难逢的机会。我们真的相信她是她这一代人的代言人。”</p><p>除了<em>《遗传厄运》</em>之外，沃尔夫最近还主演了<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/oppenheimer"><em>《奥本海默》</em></a>和<em>《寂静之地：第一天</em>》。 </p><p><iframe title="Billie Eilish: BIRDS OF A FEATHER (Live) - SNL" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/00OcH_Ktc4U?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>艾利什目前正在进行<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-announces-hit-me-hard-and-soft-world-tour-dates-in-uk-north-america-europe-and-australia-3751792">她的“Hit Me Hard and Soft”巡演</a>的北美站，该巡演将于明年夏天前往英国和爱尔兰，其中包括在伦敦 O2 体育场举行的六晚演出。您可以<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.com/billie-eilish-tickets/artist/2257710?irgwc=1&amp;clickid=36HUYSWovxyITiqQqr3h3XOTUkCW7eSoCzw9S40&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;impradid=2862475&amp;REFERRAL_ID=tmfeedbuyat2862475&amp;wt.mc_id=aff_BUYAT_2862475&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;impradname=NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;ircid=4272" target="_blank" rel="noopener">点击此处查看任何剩余的北美门票</a>，点击<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/billie-eilish-tickets/artist/2257710?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=2r0TeBxNSxyPWb32V8VL5yPRUkCW7b2kCzw9S40&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处查看英国和爱尔兰的门票</a>。</p><p>与此同时，艾利什最近分享了她得知<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rihanna">蕾哈娜</a>希望她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rihanna-names-billie-eilish-as-a-dream-collaborator-3806110">成为梦想的音乐合作者</a>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-on-being-rihannas-dream-collaborator-what-in-the-absolute-fuck-3806557">的震惊</a>。艾利什在她的 Instagram 故事中回应道：“这到底是什么操，天哪，这到底是什么操”。</p><p>上个月，艾利什在<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/saturday-night-live"><em>《周六夜现场》</em></a>中与她的兄弟芬尼斯一起<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-billie-eilish-and-finneas-join-forces-for-wildflower-and-birds-of-a-feather-on-snl-3804392">表演了她的歌曲</a>《Birds Of A Feather》和《Wildflower》 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/finneas">。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/alex-wolff-details-m